Class Summary
ActionAdapter  
And The And class denotes an event node for the composite event operator AND.
Aperiodic The Aperiodic class denotes an event node for the composite event operator APERIODIC.
AperiodicStar The AperiodicStar class denotes an event node for the composite event operator APERIODICSTAR.
Composite The Composite class is an abstract class that is extended by all composite event operator classes.
CompositeEventHandle The CompositEventHandle class denotes the event handle for a composite event.
ConditionAdapter  
Constant This class is used to keep all the constant values.
CouplingMode The CouplingMode class contains the declaration of constants denoting the three rule coupling modes defined by Sentinel.
DebuggingHelper This class contains some general purpose methods that are used by the ECAAgent.
DetectionMode This class contains the declaration of constants denoting the Detection Modes defined by the Sentinel ECAAgent.
DetectionRequestMessage The detection request message is implemented the sentinel message, containing an event of interest name, an application name in which an event has raised, a location where the application runs, and the context in which the event is detected.
ECAAgent This class contains the API to be used for Sentinel applications.
Event The abstract Event class is extended by the Primitive class and all the composite operator classes.
EventHandle The abstract EventHandle class is extended by the PrimitiveEventHandle and CompositeEventHandle classes.
EventModifier This class contains the declaration of constants denoting the event modifiers defined by Sentinel.
EventType The EventType class contains the declaration of constants denoting SNOOP event operators.
FilterAdapter  
FilterEvent  
LEDInterface The LEDInterface class is a communication module in the Local Event Detection (LED).
LEDMesgRecvImp This class implements SentinelMesgRecv.
ListOfParameterLists The ListOfParameterLists class is used to send parameters of an event to condition and action methods.It is a list of the parameter lists of the constituent primitive events.
Not The Not class denotes an event node for the composite event operator NOT.
NotificationMessage The notification message is implemented the sentinel message, containing an event of interest name, an application name in which an event has raised, a location where the application runs, and the PCTable of which the event is detected.
NotifyBuffer The NotifyBuffer class is used as a buffer that stores notifyObjects.
NotifyObject The NotifyObject class denotes an object that stores a method reference to the notify() method of a primitive event node.
Or The Or class denotes an event node for the composite event operator OR.
ParamContext The ParamContext class contains the declaration of constants denoting the four parameter contexts defined by Sentinel.
ParameterList The ParameterList class denotes the list of parameters of a primitive event.
ParaNode The ParaNode class denotes a parameter in the ParameterList.
PCEntry The PCEntry class denotes an event entry in the event table.
PCTable The PCTable class denotes an event table.
Periodic The Periodic class denotes an event node for the temporal event operator PERIODIC.
PeriodicStar The PeriodicStar class denotes an event node for the temporal event operator PERIODICSTAR.
Plus The Plus class denotes an event node for the temporal event operator PLUS.
Primitive The Primitive class is used to construct primitive event nodes for class level events, instance level events as well as temporal events.
PrimitiveEventHandle This class denotes a primitive event handle used for creating composite events and rules.
Priority The Priority class contains the declaration of some useful constants that can be used while specifying the priority for a rule.
ProcessRuleList The ProcessRuleList class denotes the list that is used to insert the rules triggered from an event.
Reactive This is a parent class of all reactive class.
RemoteEvent The remote event class is used to construct remote event nodes in the local event detection.
RemoteEventFactory The remote event factory class is provided to create the remote event node.
RemoteEventHandle This remote event handle class is used in composite event definitions.
RemoteNodeManager This class in used to manage the remote event node.
Rule The Rule class contains all the attributes of an ECA rule.
RuleScheduler The RuleScheduler class represents the rule scheduler.
Sequence The Sequence class denotes an event node for the composite event operator SEQUENCE.
Table The abstract Table class is extended by the PCTable class that denotes an event table.
TimeStamp An event (primitive or composite) is associated with a TimeStamp that denotes the time of occurrence of the event.
TriggerMode The TriggerMode class contains the declaration of constants denoting the two rule triggering modes defined by Sentinel.
Utilities This class contains some general purpose methods that are used by the ECAAgent.
